    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Benedenia fieldsi n. sp. A. Adult specimen, ventral view. Composite drawing from type material and living specimens. Abbreviations as in previous Figures. B. Accessory sclerite. C. Anterior hamulus. D. Posterior hamulus. Drawn from paratypes. Scale bars: A, 300 Μm; B – D, 25 Μm." ;
